data.description: This stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome is located in a quiet, gated community in the heart of Roswell. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining guests, and the spacious bedrooms and bathrooms provide plenty of room for everyone to relax and unwind. The main level features a large living room with a fireplace, a formal dining room, and a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, newer countertops, a wet bar, and the laundry room. The kitchen opens up to a spacious family room with a sliding glass door that leads to the private backyard. The backyard is perfect for entertaining guests or just relaxing on a hot summer day. Upstairs, there are three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The master bedroom has a private bathroom with a standing shower and a walk-in closet. The other two bedrooms are both a good size and share a bathroom. The townhome also has a two-car garage and a storage unit. The community features a lake, fishing, clubhouse, park, trails/greenway, pool, tennis courts, playgrounds and more. Near schools, shopping and nearby highways! This townhome is move-in ready and perfect for anyone looking for a luxurious and spacious home in a great location.
